CUSTOMER BASE. AS WE CONTINUE TO FOCUS ON PREMIUM PRODUCTS, THE COMPANYS PRIORITY WILL BE TO DRIVE BILLED BUSINESS AND AVERAGE SPEND PER CARD RATHER THAN ACHIEVE BROAD GROWTH IN CARDS-IN-FORCE. CORE ELEMENTS OF OUR STRATEGY ARE.

