DESIGNING CARD PRODUCTS WITH FEATURES THAT APPEAL TO TRADITIONAL AND NEWER CUSTOMER SEGMENTS



USING STRONG INCENTIVES TO DRIVE SPENDING ON OUR VARIOUS CARD PRODUCTS AND GENERATE LOYAL CUSTOMERS, INCLUDING OUR MEMBERSHIP REWARDS

