RELATIONSHIP. WE USE SOPHISTICATED CREDIT MODELS AND TECHNIQUES IN OUR RISK MANAGEMENT OPERATIONS. FOR A FURTHER DESCRIPTION OF OUR RISK MANAGEMENT POLICIES, SEE RISK MANAGEMENT

