TIME IMPROVING OPERATING MARGINS. AS MENTIONED ABOVE, J.D. POWER AND ASSOCIATES RELEASED ITS ANNUAL NATIONWIDE CREDIT CARD SATISFACTION STUDY AND RANKED AMERICAN EXPRESS HIGHEST IN OVERALL

