THE FEDERAL RIGHT TO FINANCIAL PRIVACY ACT. THE COMPANY MOVED TO COMPEL ARBITRATION ON AN INDIVIDUAL BASIS AND THE MOTION WAS GRANTED ON JANUARY 31, 2011. AN APPEAL WAS FILED ON FEBRUARY 10, 2012. COUNSEL FOR PLAINTIFFS IN

ANEKE

FILED A SIMILAR CLAIM AGAINST THE COMPANY, UNDER A DISTRICT OF COLUMBIA STATUTE, TITLED

