, PENDING IN THE SUPERIOR COURT FOR THE DISTRICT OF COLUMBIA. THE COMPANY HAS MOVED TO COMPEL

ARBITRATION IN

STEIN

. COUNSEL FOR PLAINTIFFS HAD ALSO FILED A THIRD SIMILAR ACTION,

